+# Latency Contract v1
+
+This contract standardises event-time fields across services:
+- `ts_event_ms`
+- `ts_redis_read_ms`
+- `ts_feature_ms`
+- `ts_emit_ms`
+- `ts_ws_emit_ms`
+
+Python coverage in this patch:
+- `redis_to_feature`
+- `feature_to_emit`
+- `end_to_end_event`
+
+External service contract placeholders:
+- Go ingest should publish `ts_redis_xadd_ms` and expose `ingest_to_redis` with the same stage names.
+- NestJS WS gateway should stamp `ts_ws_emit_ms` and expose `emit_to_ws`.
+
+All timestamps must be epoch milliseconds UTC. No timezone strings. No monotonic clocks in payloads.
